Files in this script generation directory:

--SCRIPT--
script_train.py         - trainig script generator, set your desired parameter settings
script_test.py          - testing script generator, set your desired parameter settings


grid_training.py        - given total training iterations, call grid_training.py
grid_testing.py         - given total testing  iterations, call grid_testing.py


run_grid_training.py    - called by grid_training.py, call simulate.py
run_grid_testing.py     - called by grid_testing.py, call simulate.py 

--TOOL--
parseResults.py         - print out training/testing results
                        - execute it without any arguments for command example

